into the main tank.

622
00:43:45,620 --> 00:43:48,214
Oh, well [Scoffs] if that's
what the chief thinks.

623
00:43:48,289 --> 00:43:51,520
So... you're gonna go out there.
You're gonna go outside.

624
00:43:51,592 --> 00:43:52,684
Yes, that's right.

625
00:43:52,760 --> 00:43:54,853
With all these... happenings
happening.

