634
00:45:29,690 --> 00:45:31,453
- [Muffled] Ooh!
- Oh, shit!

635
00:46:19,173 --> 00:46:21,971
[Gasping]

636
00:46:22,042 --> 00:46:24,374
[Gasping]

637
00:46:24,445 --> 00:46:27,642
[Gasping]

638
