00:53:24,630 --> 00:53:27,929
that is the one person
I can guarantee it's not.

736
00:53:32,371 --> 00:53:33,736
[Thudding continues]

737
00:53:38,511 --> 00:53:40,308
Don't touch me.
Don't touch me!

